
usage: s2s3 [file]

The file parameter defaults to ~/.s2s3.config.

The configuration file format is JSON.

Example configuration:

{
  "ACCESS_KEY_ID":     "MY-ACCESS-KEY",
  "ACCESS_KEY_SECRET": "MY-KEY-SECRET",
  "BUCKET":            "THE-BUCKET",
  "COPY_FORMAT":       "![{filekey}](http://THE-BUCKET.amazonaws.com/{filekey})",
  "DIRECTORY":         "my-screenshots/"
  "PREVIEW_BEFORE_UPLOAD": true
}

Required settings: ACCESS_KEY_ID, ACCESS_KEY_SECRET, BUCKET.